# Dashboard (Next.js 15) Conventions

## Tooling
- Next.js 15 with App Router (no Pages Router).
- React 19. TypeScript strict mode.
- Tailwind CSS 4 + shadcn/ui (canary).
- Laravel Echo for WebSocket subscriptions to Reverb.
- Recharts for data visualisation.

